---
title: Thai Style Pork Curry with Turmeric Rice
description: We love good Thai Pork Curry with Turmeric Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-style-pork-curry-d29092df-1fed5bec.jpg
